============================================================
8) KPI Dashboard (Track Weekly)
============================================================
Core KPIs:
1. Impressions
2. Engagement Rate = (reactions + comments + reposts + clicks) / impressions
3. Follower growth rate
4. Link Click-Through Rate
5. Profile visits from posts
6. Qualified inbound messages (demo/partnership/contributor)

Quality KPIs:
1. Technical comments ratio (signal over noise)
2. Saves per 1,000 impressions
3. Reposts by target role accounts (engineering leaders)

Target Benchmarks (initial):
- Engagement rate: 2.5%-5.0%
- Save rate: >= 0.6%
- CTR on product posts: >= 1.2%
- Follower growth: 4%-8% monthly

============================================================
9) UTM and Attribution Standards
============================================================
Use UTM links for every outbound post URL.

Template:
?utm_source=linkedin&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=nexus_launch&utm_content={post_id_or_variant}

Example:
https://github.com/Subhasis0007/nexus-hyperintelligence?utm_source=linkedin&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=nexus_q2&utm_content=deepdive_ebpf_vA

